snippet.title: NHL 17 | Official Gameplay Trailer | Xbox One, PS4
snippet.description:
Pre-Order: http://x.ea.com/8221
Play the Beta: http://x.ea.com/8224
New Features: http://x.ea.com/8225

All-new game modes, new and deeper experiences in fan-favorite modes, and the best on-ice gameplay ever make NHL 17 the most exciting EA SPORTS NHL game to date. 

Available September 13, 2016 to PS4 and Xbox One
